{"cloudId": "autodesk.atlassian.net", "pageId": "940475072", "contentFormat": "html", "versionMessage": "Add Deliverables section", "includeBody": true, "body": "<div data-local-id=\"caf9cc100819\" data-type=\"panel-info\"><p data-local-id=\"6d6d9fd52763\"><strong>Purpose:</strong> Central hub for XD work on the Products &amp; Services page within Account 3.0. Use this page for stakeholder visibility, alignment, and progress tracking.</p><p data-local-id=\"d14eeb639d2a\"><strong>Owner:</strong> Yanci Wu · <strong>Manager:</strong> Sara Mesing · <strong>Last updated:</strong> <time data-local-id=\"c0b8eb80e7d9\" datetime=\"2026-06-30\">June 30, 2026</time></p></div><p data-local-id=\"cf67358a4a60\"><strong>On this page</strong></p><p data-local-id=\"09dc12a6e5da\"><a href=\"#overview\">Overview</a> · <a href=\"#project-framing\">Project Framing</a> · <a href=\"#vision\">Vision</a> · <a href=\"#at-a-glance\">At a glance</a> · <a href=\"#strategic-tension\">Strategic tension</a> · <a href=\"#milestones\">30 / 60 / 90</a> · <a href=\"#deliverables\">Deliverables</a> · <a href=\"#top-priorities\">Priorities</a> · <a href=\"#key-stakeholders\">Stakeholders</a> · <a href=\"#account-30-context\">Account 3.0</a> · <a href=\"#decision-register\">Decision register</a> · <a href=\"#open-questions\">Open questions</a> · <a href=\"#child-pages\">Child pages</a> · <a href=\"#resources\">Resources</a></p><p data-local-id=\"4d5707b580ee\"><span data-local-id=\"83bf422a59c2\" data-type=\"inline-extension\" data-extension-key=\"anchor\" data-extension-type=\"com.atlassian.confluence.macro.core\" data-parameters=\"{&quot;macroParams&quot;:{&quot;&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;overview&quot;},&quot;legacyAnchorId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Products&amp;amp;ServicesExperienceEvolution–XDHub-overview&quot;}},&quot;macroMetadata&quot;:{&quot;macroId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;9ecc3e55-5644-4625-bf57-fe25af5a97cc&quot;},&quot;schemaVersion&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;1&quot;},&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Anchor&quot;}}\"></span></p><h2 data-local-id=\"21d23876117d\">Overview</h2><p data-local-id=\"546c981db0fd\">This page is the central hub for the Experience Design work supporting the evolution of the Products &amp; Services experience within Autodesk Account Portal. It serves as the single source of truth, communication hub, decision log, roadmap, and knowledge base.</p><p data-local-id=\"d0b80c4d8900\"><span data-local-id=\"f19dd83f09c5\" data-type=\"inline-extension\" data-extension-key=\"anchor\" data-extension-type=\"com.atlassian.confluence.macro.core\" data-parameters=\"{&quot;macroParams&quot;:{&quot;&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;project-framing&quot;},&quot;legacyAnchorId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Products&amp;amp;ServicesExperienceEvolution–XDHub-project-framing&quot;}},&quot;macroMetadata&quot;:{&quot;macroId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;644a0d1f-ad62-4b89-8754-cd088c1840b0&quot;},&quot;schemaVersion&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;1&quot;},&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Anchor&quot;}}\"></span></p><h2 data-local-id=\"936540f3d837\">Project Framing</h2><p data-local-id=\"1d440794f9b6\">The Products &amp; Services experience intersects Account 3.0, product fulfillment modernization, ecosystem expansion, marketplace integration, AI-enabled experiences, and cross-divisional experience architecture. This project establishes a clear point of view on the role of P&amp;S within that ecosystem.</p><p data-local-id=\"9c78ac52f10d\"><span data-local-id=\"af1a9a4a88fb\" data-type=\"inline-extension\" data-extension-key=\"anchor\" data-extension-type=\"com.atlassian.confluence.macro.core\" data-parameters=\"{&quot;macroParams&quot;:{&quot;&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;vision&quot;},&quot;legacyAnchorId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Products&amp;amp;ServicesExperienceEvolution–XDHub-vision&quot;}},&quot;macroMetadata&quot;:{&quot;macroId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;609d133b-d3d1-4625-a2b6-18284baec971&quot;},&quot;schemaVersion&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;1&quot;},&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Anchor&quot;}}\"></span></p><h2 data-local-id=\"d74f5c023d3d\">Vision</h2><p data-local-id=\"255dc4e50f74\">Evolve Products &amp; Services from a product fulfillment page into a Capability Control Center where administrators can discover, deploy, govern, and manage Autodesk products, marketplace solutions, AI agents, workflow automations, and future capabilities.</p><p data-local-id=\"497c0997133d\"><span data-local-id=\"15544d229221\" data-type=\"inline-extension\" data-extension-key=\"anchor\" data-extension-type=\"com.atlassian.confluence.macro.core\" data-parameters=\"{&quot;macroParams&quot;:{&quot;&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;at-a-glance&quot;},&quot;legacyAnchorId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Products&amp;amp;ServicesExperienceEvolution–XDHub-at-a-glance&quot;}},&quot;macroMetadata&quot;:{&quot;macroId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;6bfd9a3d-79d3-4f9e-9fa9-c23dfa23be66&quot;},&quot;schemaVersion&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;1&quot;},&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Anchor&quot;}}\"></span></p><h2 data-local-id=\"555da05b76a1\">Strategic tension (core of this work)</h2><p data-local-id=\"e66e66dc1428\">Three directions exist and must be reconciled in the XD POV:</p><table data-local-id=\"189302ac0b30\" data-width=\"760\"><thead><tr><th data-local-id=\"485f37e00717\"><p data-local-id=\"351966883de5\">Lens</p></th><th data-local-id=\"191744657fac\"><p data-local-id=\"8be36de765c2\">Source</p></th><th data-local-id=\"068701c9928d\"><p data-local-id=\"a168d87979fb\">Direction</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td data-local-id=\"9a6b2f218b8e\"><p data-local-id=\"4fed01b77beb\">Ecosystem expansion</p></td><td data-local-id=\"f8250a7b57f9\"><p data-local-id=\"5a74f250cdb0\"><a href=\"https://autodesk.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/~krishnbh/pages/862634571\">Bharath P&amp;S PRD</a></p></td><td data-local-id=\"dbd461f00994\"><p data-local-id=\"2f363d46dbc0\">Evolve P&amp;S to Products &amp; Solutions: marketplace discovery, AI agents, trust signals, admin approval</p></td></tr><tr><td data-local-id=\"78dd38e928f4\"><p data-local-id=\"61d74f685320\">Fulfillment focus</p></td><td data-local-id=\"0a0d383596e8\"><p data-local-id=\"995470d472fc\"><a href=\"https://pages.git.autodesk.com/subrampr/ps-guide/\">Designer’s Field Guide</a></p></td><td data-local-id=\"a9291472fc9e\"><p data-local-id=\"e07f14abec26\">P&amp;S stays fulfillment-only; ecosystem is a separate capability domain in the Capability Control Center</p></td></tr><tr><td data-local-id=\"d3b91e348944\"><p data-local-id=\"33381c035ec6\">Portal personalization</p></td><td data-local-id=\"1cdfd36ed7d0\"><p data-local-id=\"d45b8a148036\"><a href=\"https://share.autodesk.com/:w:/r/sites/Account3.0/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B78100E36-5A1C-4A70-B545-886F5D46FF6A%7D&amp;file=PRD%20-%20MVP%20R05%20Account%203.0.docx&amp;action=default&amp;mobileredirect=true\">Account 3.0 PDR</a></p><p data-local-id=\"434fd5caa000\"><a href=\"https://share.autodesk.com/:p:/s/Account3.0/EVVzkR6gkkRNmMrRh01RWE8Bh2WVYqkp8xXXonaflS0nag?e=rPi4iD\">Account 3.0 deck</a></p></td><td data-local-id=\"41727ec2dbdf\"><p data-local-id=\"36cfd7523dd2\">Product-centric job surface with dynamic learning, community, and recommendations woven in</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p data-local-id=\"73bbbe75dd53\"><span data-local-id=\"acb703e35525\" data-type=\"inline-extension\" data-extension-key=\"anchor\" data-extension-type=\"com.atlassian.confluence.macro.core\" data-parameters=\"{&quot;macroParams&quot;:{&quot;&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;milestones&quot;},&quot;legacyAnchorId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Products&amp;amp;ServicesExperienceEvolution–XDHub-milestones&quot;}},&quot;macroMetadata&quot;:{&quot;macroId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;a3af20f4-05bc-47ef-aed8-9519eed2bf66&quot;},&quot;schemaVersion&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;1&quot;},&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Anchor&quot;}}\"></span></p><h2 data-local-id=\"c01fe17191f1\">30 / 60 / 90 milestones</h2><table data-local-id=\"d4411c0df756\" data-width=\"760\"><thead><tr><th data-local-id=\"dea0aa01dd57\"><p data-local-id=\"0cf8faca328d\">Horizon</p></th><th data-local-id=\"4d8817350554\"><p data-local-id=\"b96cfcb52ccb\">Date</p></th><th data-local-id=\"07c3ec914dfa\"><p data-local-id=\"3234bc863d2f\">Deliverable</p></th><th data-local-id=\"3862546d8d2b\"><p data-local-id=\"5fe1f2226e9e\">Status</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td data-local-id=\"7e4e447bad7b\"><p data-local-id=\"454fc5e04011\"><strong>30 days</strong></p></td><td data-local-id=\"2a02a67b65cb\"><p data-local-id=\"21c0e7a2c0f2\">Aug 4</p></td><td data-local-id=\"548272b68e5e\"><p data-local-id=\"509ae251862f\">Frame problem; clarify P&amp;S role; v0.1 scope boundary; customer evidence plan</p></td><td data-local-id=\"2a00205a484e\"><p data-local-id=\"59b015ce20a6\"><span data-local-id=\"b312f1bd-1197-4955-ae76-b40c66bac33d\" data-type=\"status\" data-color=\"blue\">In progress</span></p></td></tr><tr><td data-local-id=\"6fd83beac12c\"><p data-local-id=\"cb74b0c0da50\"><strong>60 days</strong></p></td><td data-local-id=\"e0d980454e3d\"><p data-local-id=\"2fe2263fb629\">Sept 16</p></td><td data-local-id=\"9ddc5a3e4193\"><p data-local-id=\"a7488c11e9a2\">Leadership-ready XD POV (before AU); install/update experience map</p></td><td data-local-id=\"d4ed1369fb4d\"><p data-local-id=\"2e51ff7178c3\"><span data-local-id=\"888542b8-c712-4bc4-b6ad-6b30b6bee8a9\" data-type=\"status\" data-color=\"neutral\">Not started</span></p></td></tr><tr><td data-local-id=\"0ee41918bd1d\"><p data-local-id=\"beb47ff63a63\"><strong>90 days</strong></p></td><td data-local-id=\"fec7d6e53300\"><p data-local-id=\"d72949dc23db\">Oct 27</p></td><td data-local-id=\"7a21638f9af5\"><p data-local-id=\"826fb00a9dd6\">Execution operating model — decision rights, risks, near-term design plan</p></td><td data-local-id=\"15f2ba6e5a97\"><p data-local-id=\"dcf8e09181a5\"><span data-local-id=\"0b5de284-76d4-48dd-80a1-70dacd9fd5bc\" data-type=\"status\" data-color=\"neutral\">Not started</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span data-type=\"inline-extension\" data-extension-key=\"anchor\" data-extension-type=\"com.atlassian.confluence.macro.core\" data-parameters=\"{&quot;macroParams&quot;:{&quot;&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;deliverables&quot;}},&quot;macroMetadata&quot;:{&quot;schemaVersion&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;1&quot;},&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Anchor&quot;}}\"></span></p><h2>Deliverables</h2><p>Concrete XD outputs mapped to 30 / 60 / 90 horizons. Link artifacts as they ship.</p><table data-width=\"760\"><thead><tr><th><p>Deliverable</p></th><th><p>Horizon</p></th><th><p>Target</p></th><th><p>Status</p></th><th><p>Link</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>P&amp;S scope boundary (v0.1)</p></td><td><p>30 days</p></td><td><p>Aug 4</p></td><td><p><span data-type=\"status\" data-color=\"blue\">In progress</span></p></td><td><p>—</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Customer evidence plan</p></td><td><p>30 days</p></td><td><p>Aug 4</p></td><td><p><span data-type=\"status\" data-color=\"neutral\">Not started</span></p></td><td><p>—</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Stakeholder interview synthesis</p></td><td><p>30 days</p></td><td><p>Aug 4</p></td><td><p><span data-type=\"status\" data-color=\"blue\">In progress</span></p></td><td><p><a href=\"https://autodesk.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/~wuya/pages/940475182\">Stakeholder Interviews</a></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Leadership-ready XD POV</p></td><td><p>60 days</p></td><td><p>Sept 16</p></td><td><p><span data-type=\"status\" data-color=\"neutral\">Not started</span></p></td><td><p>—</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Install/update experience map (current → future)</p></td><td><p>60 days</p></td><td><p>Sept 16</p></td><td><p><span data-type=\"status\" data-color=\"neutral\">Not started</span></p></td><td><p>—</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Cross-divisional partnership model</p></td><td><p>60–90 days</p></td><td><p>Oct 27</p></td><td><p><span data-type=\"status\" data-color=\"neutral\">Not started</span></p></td><td><p>—</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Execution operating model</p></td><td><p>90 days</p></td><td><p>Oct 27</p></td><td><p><span data-type=\"status\" data-color=\"neutral\">Not started</span></p></td><td><p>—</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p data-local-id=\"535dd2da0bb0\"><span data-local-id=\"883315970723\" data-type=\"inline-extension\" data-extension-key=\"anchor\" data-extension-type=\"com.atlassian.confluence.macro.core\" data-parameters=\"{&quot;macroParams&quot;:{&quot;&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;top-priorities&quot;},&quot;legacyAnchorId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Products&amp;amp;ServicesExperienceEvolution–XDHub-top-priorities&quot;}},&quot;macroMetadata&quot;:{&quot;macroId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;55cee0dc-3c23-4a52-8b95-e4ce945dba1d&quot;},&quot;schemaVersion&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;1&quot;},&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Anchor&quot;}}\"></span></p><h2 data-local-id=\"7a96548fb715\">Top priorities</h2><ul data-local-id=\"d284eb28f41b\" data-type=\"task-list\"><li data-local-id=\"116230e6f4e6\" data-type=\"task-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Own the P&amp;S product-area POV (what belongs / what does not)</li><li data-local-id=\"1c2b5278edda\" data-type=\"task-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Define install/update current to future experience map</li><li data-local-id=\"54dba9e420e8\" data-type=\"task-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Build cross-divisional partnership model</li><li data-local-id=\"7dc6d93b235e\" data-type=\"task-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Ship visible artifacts early</li></ul><p data-local-id=\"99b9f5b9879a\"><span data-local-id=\"19c75179f51f\" data-type=\"inline-extension\" data-extension-key=\"anchor\" data-extension-type=\"com.atlassian.confluence.macro.core\" data-parameters=\"{&quot;macroParams&quot;:{&quot;&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;key-stakeholders&quot;},&quot;legacyAnchorId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Products&amp;amp;ServicesExperienceEvolution–XDHub-key-stakeholders&quot;}},&quot;macroMetadata&quot;:{&quot;macroId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;b31db232-c95a-4c9b-a1ec-9e18a3111d05&quot;},&quot;schemaVersion&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;1&quot;},&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Anchor&quot;}}\"></span></p><h2 data-local-id=\"955d0407bb04\">Key stakeholders</h2><table data-local-id=\"d2d5256019ed\" data-width=\"760\"><thead><tr><th data-local-id=\"c37b38ad9254\"><p data-local-id=\"b1aeacd4f157\">Name</p></th><th data-local-id=\"4490e99a3b5b\"><p data-local-id=\"209e0e5ca7b0\">Team</p></th><th data-local-id=\"dcfe6b33d3bf\"><p data-local-id=\"35b223e66856\">Role in this work</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td data-local-id=\"0c71fd5abe66\"><p data-local-id=\"128738e77945\">Sara Mesing</p></td><td data-local-id=\"3ad6632b16d8\"><p data-local-id=\"f91f971bd950\">PSET-DE XD</p></td><td data-local-id=\"560b068a154c\"><p data-local-id=\"a206a00952dc\">Manager; Account 3.0 governance and Experience Architecture</p></td></tr><tr><td data-local-id=\"c884e0ad2f44\"><p data-local-id=\"3b6da5db9906\">Bharath Krishnan</p></td><td data-local-id=\"34039ddaf7c3\"><p data-local-id=\"ea3147a8a0ee\">DE PM</p></td><td data-local-id=\"f25eac2c1d2e\"><p data-local-id=\"17309ec64af6\">P&amp;S page PM; strategic vision PRD</p></td></tr><tr><td data-local-id=\"b2525d158581\"><p data-local-id=\"c2c95cd58ec5\">Rob Westwood</p></td><td data-local-id=\"edfd982310af\"><p data-local-id=\"46261d4575c5\">PSET-DE</p></td><td data-local-id=\"527cf6feaf3e\"><p data-local-id=\"69a889c8ef40\">Cross-division tradeoff negotiations</p></td></tr><tr><td data-local-id=\"b7ddacf89c31\"><p data-local-id=\"20677412eea4\">Prada</p></td><td data-local-id=\"10b66cf38fc6\"><p data-local-id=\"8c1a67016be1\">PSET-DE XD (Singapore)</p></td><td data-local-id=\"64658f2c1003\"><p data-local-id=\"f459f6f7dd66\">Designer Field Guide</p></td></tr><tr><td data-local-id=\"235906d6ce3c\"><p data-local-id=\"cdac7a839aea\">Swati Chowdhury</p></td><td data-local-id=\"c566b1d71b95\"><p data-local-id=\"632ca2801502\">COO-DEC / GET CS</p></td><td data-local-id=\"43febee70e62\"><p data-local-id=\"f51019082d61\">Account 3.0 PM</p></td></tr><tr><td data-local-id=\"3024215a4256\"><p data-local-id=\"f19020362a4c\">Mark Blackman / James Schmittler</p></td><td data-local-id=\"8390ad1b719a\"><p data-local-id=\"32f25b8aad30\">Signed-In Growth</p></td><td data-local-id=\"26e4d75d5dfe\"><p data-local-id=\"e95788ec14f8\">Post-purchase value realization experiments</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p data-local-id=\"a1d7b89ec455\"><span data-local-id=\"3de6fb35a03f\" data-type=\"inline-extension\" data-extension-key=\"anchor\" data-extension-type=\"com.atlassian.confluence.macro.core\" data-parameters=\"{&quot;macroParams&quot;:{&quot;&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;account-30-context&quot;},&quot;legacyAnchorId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Products&amp;amp;ServicesExperienceEvolution–XDHub-account-30-context&quot;}},&quot;macroMetadata&quot;:{&quot;macroId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;e2f57f41-fa77-45e8-866c-9284cb5d66cf&quot;},&quot;schemaVersion&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;1&quot;},&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Anchor&quot;}}\"></span></p><h2 data-local-id=\"a60e90630bce\">Account 3.0 context (what is shipping now)</h2><ul data-local-id=\"d4cdb135b00e\"><li data-local-id=\"6aeaa886925f\"><p data-local-id=\"a5719c6d0f93\"><strong>R0.5 MVP:</strong> Guided post-purchase gateway for Reach single-seat Fusion + Inventor Pro (NAMER). North star = time-to-download.</p></li><li data-local-id=\"838b111a2771\"><p data-local-id=\"7d988c19c9ed\"><strong>Q1 result:</strong> Fusion experiment won (+8.6pp download within 30 min at 92% confidence).</p></li><li data-local-id=\"daf892cce858\"><p data-local-id=\"e6f3fe288c3e\"><strong>Q2 experiments:</strong> Native billing, trial experience, ML learn, micro-admin (2-5 seats).</p></li><li data-local-id=\"282985a7bc12\"><p data-local-id=\"a819b7dc8006\"><strong>P&amp;S in R0.5:</strong> Beta surface + legacy bridge — not a full P&amp;S redesign. Heavy install/update scope deferred to multi-seat phase (TBD).</p></li><li data-local-id=\"b4a341243539\"><p data-local-id=\"68af82aa63cc\"><strong>Account 2.5:</strong> AEM retirement track; experience unchanged; fallback for non-beta users.</p></li></ul><p data-local-id=\"1d2db1e8f54a\"><span data-local-id=\"602b998b721e\" data-type=\"inline-extension\" data-extension-key=\"anchor\" data-extension-type=\"com.atlassian.confluence.macro.core\" data-parameters=\"{&quot;macroParams&quot;:{&quot;&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;decision-register&quot;},&quot;legacyAnchorId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Products&amp;amp;ServicesExperienceEvolution–XDHub-decision-register&quot;}},&quot;macroMetadata&quot;:{&quot;macroId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;931e1b86-4dfd-49d4-b75d-84273f20be5a&quot;},&quot;schemaVersion&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;1&quot;},&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Anchor&quot;}}\"></span></p><h2 data-local-id=\"93fc112a0dcb\">Decision register</h2><p data-local-id=\"bd34ec5e357a\">Tracked decisions with owners, status, and target dates. Update as alignment conversations happen.</p><table data-local-id=\"661ba8c657f7\" data-width=\"760\"><thead><tr><th data-local-id=\"621e8835e06c\"><p data-local-id=\"fc52821a47a3\">Decision</p></th><th data-local-id=\"8d2e826ea6be\"><p data-local-id=\"b86a0c126d2f\">Options / context</p></th><th data-local-id=\"c52045d6e8a4\"><p data-local-id=\"88ca394cd94e\">Owner</p></th><th data-local-id=\"3d8a501371d5\"><p data-local-id=\"04278b5ddf54\">Status</p></th><th data-local-id=\"3dec74bd9597\"><p data-local-id=\"86dd6e4d7ec4\">Target date</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td data-local-id=\"0e8111f09f25\"><p data-local-id=\"fd9a2fa31807\">Job of P&amp;S page</p></td><td data-local-id=\"4cf020f52f52\"><p data-local-id=\"b5f48fbac90f\">Fulfillment-only vs. solution hub with marketplace</p></td><td data-local-id=\"6e31969ef0cb\"><p data-local-id=\"397d378a0cfd\">XD + PM</p></td><td data-local-id=\"570547106191\"><p data-local-id=\"8e3df2c4fe50\"><span data-local-id=\"691d58cc-7d96-4218-851a-161f8ee2ba71\" data-type=\"status\" data-color=\"yellow\">In progress</span></p></td><td data-local-id=\"5db71c60b703\"><p data-local-id=\"2cd0c0d6d608\">Aug 2026</p></td></tr><tr><td data-local-id=\"85ba1bb88e19\"><p data-local-id=\"af2597c5013b\">Marketplace on P&amp;S vs. adjacent surfaces</p></td><td data-local-id=\"5e1c3587faf0\"><p data-local-id=\"2e68789583a3\">Product detail recommendations vs. dedicated Marketplace page</p></td><td data-local-id=\"21f9c0e35321\"><p data-local-id=\"c36c8acec3a8\">XD + COO-DEC</p></td><td data-local-id=\"26ab45553482\"><p data-local-id=\"81c6277438c0\"><span data-local-id=\"b73eacbc-6860-42ca-a0b8-f9ee64ec46c0\" data-type=\"status\" data-color=\"neutral\">Not started</span></p></td><td data-local-id=\"877ef5e3948b\"><p data-local-id=\"00865f9940e7\">Sept 2026</p></td></tr><tr><td data-local-id=\"e176b7171741\"><p data-local-id=\"6680db3b2dc0\">Naming: P&amp;S vs. Products &amp; Solutions</p></td><td data-local-id=\"256b9d499751\"><p data-local-id=\"e38637fd2c8e\">Bharath PRD proposes rename; Sara vision uses Capability Control Center framing</p></td><td data-local-id=\"9b16aa284dcb\"><p data-local-id=\"a8cc232a2862\">PM + XD + leadership</p></td><td data-local-id=\"10b39798ed28\"><p data-local-id=\"a5effc8c06ed\"><span data-local-id=\"33633d1d-be6c-4e48-9bb7-e33dfb441672\" data-type=\"status\" data-color=\"neutral\">Not started</span></p></td><td data-local-id=\"6a10b4da7cb7\"><p data-local-id=\"59be59303b0a\">TBD</p></td></tr><tr><td data-local-id=\"2925ff3de1d8\"><p data-local-id=\"86674cdd446e\">Install/update modernization scope</p></td><td data-local-id=\"a4fdbf9b6152\"><p data-local-id=\"d7c656b22c6b\">Agentic flows; trust model for AI-powered installs</p></td><td data-local-id=\"18aa74c98a9c\"><p data-local-id=\"e49da1cd2bae\">XD + Eng</p></td><td data-local-id=\"007b78bcc78a\"><p data-local-id=\"dbc450cd228d\"><span data-local-id=\"fa24a67d-d86a-445b-8151-6747715d2aa0\" data-type=\"status\" data-color=\"neutral\">Not started</span></p></td><td data-local-id=\"3c126d81821a\"><p data-local-id=\"e8d61b03836b\">Oct 2026</p></td></tr><tr><td data-local-id=\"ae4fdfc8a65e\"><p data-local-id=\"cbd28e0fdc46\">Integration contract for P&amp;S slots</p></td><td data-local-id=\"584fddd05acb\"><p data-local-id=\"2e85373edadb\">How P&amp;S composes within Account 3.0 IA</p></td><td data-local-id=\"01a0c8eca382\"><p data-local-id=\"f1fa8116a1c6\">Sara (EA) + XD</p></td><td data-local-id=\"62f9b8a2a2f9\"><p data-local-id=\"b5f646771ed4\"><span data-local-id=\"4765e908-0b90-45ed-8188-7592e1bf9ac9\" data-type=\"status\" data-color=\"neutral\">Not started</span></p></td><td data-local-id=\"39135f52b4fd\"><p data-local-id=\"a842aed92a39\">TBD</p></td></tr><tr><td data-local-id=\"c42848d790dc\"><p data-local-id=\"b7b39cdccef6\">Now vs. later for P&amp;S Phase 1</p></td><td data-local-id=\"050afb5be5c9\"><p data-local-id=\"4439a5b7a287\">Trust badges, Assistant entry, marketplace modules on product cards</p></td><td data-local-id=\"882f88327281\"><p data-local-id=\"e60dbf93bb62\">XD + PM</p></td><td data-local-id=\"456258d6ede9\"><p data-local-id=\"2e89592e399c\"><span data-local-id=\"2672f99f-3e3b-4f59-b023-3ac641c6d679\" data-type=\"status\" data-color=\"neutral\">Not started</span></p></td><td data-local-id=\"3f6d7d6ee38b\"><p data-local-id=\"223e7cf39e15\">Pre-AU</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p data-local-id=\"b2e44ff19987\"><span data-local-id=\"8a5cdbcb37bf\" data-type=\"inline-extension\" data-extension-key=\"anchor\" data-extension-type=\"com.atlassian.confluence.macro.core\" data-parameters=\"{&quot;macroParams&quot;:{&quot;&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;open-questions&quot;},&quot;legacyAnchorId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Products&amp;amp;ServicesExperienceEvolution–XDHub-open-questions&quot;}},&quot;macroMetadata&quot;:{&quot;macroId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;0022f34e-58b6-4138-9ef9-58878181c110&quot;},&quot;schemaVersion&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;1&quot;},&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Anchor&quot;}}\"></span></p><h2 data-local-id=\"1797fde601e1\">Open questions</h2><details data-local-id=\"e10cba9bcef7\" data-breakout=\"wide\" data-breakout-width=\"760\"><summary>POV questions to answer</summary><ul data-local-id=\"801441cf20fc\" data-type=\"decision-list\"><li data-local-id=\"539b055aa92f\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">What is the job of the P&amp;S page?</li><li data-local-id=\"92439638bcca\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">What belongs on the P&amp;S page?</li><li data-local-id=\"dcbf961b4313\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">What does not belong on the P&amp;S page?</li><li data-local-id=\"0a77b9188818\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">What belongs on P&amp;S vs. adjacent Account 3.0 surfaces (Home, Learn, Marketplace)?</li><li data-local-id=\"da9407ce70c0\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">How should download, install, and update work in the modernized experience?</li><li data-local-id=\"d7b278889ccd\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">How should we incorporate access points to ecosystem offerings (3rd-party apps, AI agents, MCPs, workflow recommendations)?</li><li data-local-id=\"f725f3ba1e5b\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">How do ecosystem access points connect without bloating P&amp;S?</li><li data-local-id=\"3ae2fcdc00a3\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">What should change now vs. later?</li><li data-local-id=\"a0601cc595f1\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">What decisions do we need from leadership?</li></ul></details><details data-local-id=\"f4a1b2fb883e\" data-breakout=\"wide\" data-breakout-width=\"760\"><summary>Product strategy and evidence</summary><ul data-local-id=\"b8a273ec47c5\" data-type=\"decision-list\"><li data-local-id=\"f44a06d69a05\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">What customer outcomes should P&amp;S own?</li><li data-local-id=\"e33dbcb197e6\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">What evidence supports the vision?</li><li data-local-id=\"2e6b3ffdf332\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">What is driving the new P&amp;S page — user needs, business needs, or technical needs?</li><li data-local-id=\"4970f5ed90b9\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">What is the vision based on? What user research has been done for this page redesign?</li><li data-local-id=\"96e6e18588d7\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">Is time-to-download still the right NSM for P&amp;S given Reach research?</li><li data-local-id=\"4b019792a334\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">What research gaps need a lightweight evidence plan?</li></ul></details><details data-local-id=\"8bb4b7ba68ec\" data-breakout=\"wide\" data-breakout-width=\"760\"><summary>Scope and field guide</summary><ul data-local-id=\"dfa701bbadc3\" data-type=\"decision-list\"><li data-local-id=\"27c0612f2838\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">Should we preserve the design decisions in the P&amp;S page as listed in the <a href=\"https://pages.git.autodesk.com/subrampr/ps-guide/#what\">P&amp;S Field Guide</a>? Where to find the rationales?</li><li data-local-id=\"cfcc38deb9f5\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">The new vision lists many new capabilities — do they all belong on the P&amp;S page? (e.g., does usage belong on the usage reporting page or P&amp;S? Does discovery belong on .com or P&amp;S?)</li><li data-local-id=\"47d71d686d1b\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">How much marketplace/ecosystem surfaces on P&amp;S vs. adjacent Account 3.0 pages?</li><li data-local-id=\"676c7d24a18c\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">What ships in Account 3.0 MVP vs. multi-seat phase vs. post-AU?</li><li data-local-id=\"3f67aa05f209\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">Who owns product detail page recommendations — fulfillment or ecosystem UX?</li></ul></details><details data-local-id=\"91ec5af97196\" data-breakout=\"wide\" data-breakout-width=\"760\"><summary>Account 3.0 alignment</summary><ul data-local-id=\"29ec0a56658c\" data-type=\"decision-list\"><li data-local-id=\"aba3b2801725\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">What is the vision of Account 3.0?</li><li data-local-id=\"b5a2cf4180bb\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">What is the status of Account 3.0?</li><li data-local-id=\"78e40e1622c8\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">How does P&amp;S align with Account 3.0?</li><li data-local-id=\"4ab42e443983\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">What dependencies and milestones exist?</li><li data-local-id=\"a3adee72dae3\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">Is the Account 3.0 Products page intended to be the Products &amp; Services page? Is it being designed already?</li><li data-local-id=\"fbbba1f80f3d\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">What is the Account 3.0 timeline? How does the new P&amp;S page fit into that timeline?</li><li data-local-id=\"06d0dd1204d3\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">Is Account 3.0 being rolled out in stages? Is the first stage for Reach customers?</li><li data-local-id=\"04cd5da1541d\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">What is locked in Account 3.0 vs. still shifting?</li></ul></details><details data-local-id=\"992da8178044\" data-breakout=\"wide\" data-breakout-width=\"760\"><summary>Install and update</summary><ul data-local-id=\"763c647537f0\" data-type=\"decision-list\"><li data-local-id=\"480278653eee\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">What does modernized install/update mean for agentic flows?</li><li data-local-id=\"41888adab66b\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">What is the trust model for AI/predictive installs?</li><li data-local-id=\"f0be1ffc9c97\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">When does heavy P&amp;S scope (Manage Install and Updates) land?</li></ul></details><details data-local-id=\"95ccb07183cd\" data-breakout=\"wide\" data-breakout-width=\"760\"><summary>Operating model and cross-divisional partnership</summary><ul data-local-id=\"65c20b0af57e\" data-type=\"decision-list\"><li data-local-id=\"5d540248962b\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">Who decides IA slots and cross-team tradeoffs?</li><li data-local-id=\"2040c6549419\" data-type=\"decision-item\" data-state=\"UNDECIDED\">How do multiple teams ship independently while preserving a coherent customer experience?</li></ul></details><details data-local-id=\"950ab1b9c985\" data-breakout=\"wide\" data-breakout-width=\"760\"><summary>Leadership decisions needed</summary><ul data-local-id=\"c127812c1734\" data-type=\"task-list\"><li data-local-id=\"35ae22a55455\" data-type=\"task-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Endorse P&amp;S fulfillment-first scope boundary</li><li data-local-id=\"e7cc241efb86\" data-type=\"task-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Align on now vs. later for ecosystem features on product pages</li><li data-local-id=\"6b7ba4a0152e\" data-type=\"task-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Confirm P&amp;S ownership in Account 3.0 integration contract</li><li data-local-id=\"036bb5df0383\" data-type=\"task-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Greenlight install/update experience map direction pre-AU</li></ul></details><p data-local-id=\"0cd2e9b2a1b3\"><span data-local-id=\"15f38bb9ffa4\" data-type=\"inline-extension\" data-extension-key=\"anchor\" data-extension-type=\"com.atlassian.confluence.macro.core\" data-parameters=\"{&quot;macroParams&quot;:{&quot;&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;child-pages&quot;},&quot;legacyAnchorId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Products&amp;amp;ServicesExperienceEvolution–XDHub-child-pages&quot;}},&quot;macroMetadata&quot;:{&quot;macroId&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;2ebcfbec-02ac-4b8b-bef0-742ac47e3ff3&quot;},&quot;schemaVersion&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;1&quot;},&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Anchor&quot;}}\"></span></p><h2 data-local-id=\"788f097a5aa8\">Resources</h2><ul data-local-id=\"0a7e6876dfd3\"><li data-local-id=\"af31cf11937d\"><p data-local-id=\"2e97a024f903\"><a href=\"https://autodesk.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/~krishnbh/pages/862634571\">Strategic vision for the Autodesk Products and Services page in the Manage portal</a> — Bharath Krishnan (PM)</p></li><li data-local-id=\"84113ca10375\"><p data-local-id=\"e430b5f55abe\"><a href=\"https://myshare.autodesk.com/:w:/g/personal/sara_mesing_autodesk_com/IQDD38jpgfiNSaigb6YzfZYTAeFG9sTswo2LyDDnxuyGqFY?e=CiViaX\">Evolving Account Portal into a Capability Control Center</a> — Sara Mesing (UX Vision)</p></li><li data-local-id=\"601090ef351b\"><p data-local-id=\"bcc4d8d01d96\"><a href=\"https://pages.git.autodesk.com/subrampr/ps-guide/#what\">P&amp;S Field Guide</a> — Prada (requires VPN)</p></li><li data-local-id=\"7bab2f6333b5\"><p data-local-id=\"171c8515cd5a\"><a href=\"https://autodesk.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/EFD/pages/442724635\">Account 3.0 wiki</a></p></li><li data-local-id=\"41733f66880d\"><p data-local-id=\"3eb25eedf85d\"><a href=\"https://share.autodesk.com/:p:/s/Account3.0/EVVzkR6gkkRNmMrRh01RWE8Bh2WVYqkp8xXXonaflS0nag?e=rPi4iD\">Account 3.0 deck</a></p></li><li data-local-id=\"f27a21092dad\"><p data-local-id=\"f180f7792fbc\"><a href=\"https://share.autodesk.com/:w:/r/sites/Account3.0/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B78100E36-5A1C-4A70-B545-886F5D46FF6A%7D&amp;file=PRD%20-%20MVP%20R05%20Account%203.0.docx&amp;action=default&amp;mobileredirect=true\">Account 3.0 PRD</a></p></li><li data-local-id=\"d4770b78921a\"><p data-local-id=\"ead5610dc404\"><a href=\"https://www.brainshark.com/1/player/autodeskinc?pi=zIFzGkcQEzrLwUz0&amp;r3f1=B08AF4A7ABA6FEECBCE097F4BCBFB0B7A8BDE096ECB2A8A6ADA2FDAF8CE5A7F4\">Account 3.0 executive pitch</a></p></li></ul><p data-local-id=\"59ebd2c7e76c\">See also <a href=\"https://autodesk.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/~wuya/pages/945258583\">Resource Library</a> for local docs, research highlights, and release phases.</p>"}